Package: covWt
Title: Spatial covariance weighting in R
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Benjamin", "Misiuk", , "benjaminmisiuk@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
URL: https://github.com/benjaminmisiuk/covWt
Description: The package provides code and functions to calculate spatial covariance weights, e.g., for bagging and spatial validation. Companion to the manusctript "Improved environmental mapping and validation using bagging models with spatially clustered data" by Misiuk & Brown (2022).
